text: It's cool, their company appreciates the hobby of its artists, especially Sakura, here Hybe really facilitates her to develop her work, so it turns out that in their company, it's not only idol-like talents that are supported, but also other talents from the idols themselves, such as Sakura with her knitting talent. Hybe deserves to maintain a top company because by freeing or supporting their idols' hobbies, more job opportunities will be opened from this, for example, if Sakura ends up knitting, Hybe and her agency will also add other people to collaborate in knitting, so there are opportunities for other people to collaborate.
